Ben Conway is an illustrator, skilled at using 3D modeling and traditional media to create visually interesting and scientifically accurate images of a variety of subjects, including spacecraft and astronomical objects.
Ben has had an illustration-related internship at Caltech&rsquo;s Jet Propulsion Laboratory. He has also participated in the Psyche Inspired  internship program run by Arizona State University in connection with NASA&rsquo;s Psyche mission.
